              What is your refund policy?
            </button>
          </h3>
          <div id="paymentCollapse3" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="paymentHeading3" data-bs-parent="#paymentAccordion">
            <div class="accordion-body">
              <p>Our refund policy is designed to be fair to both passengers and drivers:</p>
              <ul>
                <li><strong>Cancellation by passenger:</strong>
                  <ul>
                    <li>Free if cancelled within 2 minutes of request</li>
                    <li>RM 3 fee if cancelled after 2 minutes but before driver arrives</li>
                    <li>50% of fare if cancelled after driver arrives</li>
                  </ul>
                </li>
                <li><strong>Cancellation by driver:</strong> Full refund to passenger</li>
                <li><strong>Service issues:</strong> Full or partial refund depending on the nature of the issue</li>
              </ul>
              <p>To request a refund, go to your "Ride History," select the ride in question, and click "Report an Issue." Our support team will review your request within 24 hours.</p>
